jsat.datatransform

Interface DataTransformFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BDS.BDSFactory, LinearTransform.LinearTransformFactory, LRS.LRSFactory, MutualInfoFS.MutualInfoFSFactory, NominalToNumeric.NominalToNumericTransformFactory, NumericalToHistogram.NumericalToHistogramTransformFactory, PCA.PCAFactory, PNormNormalization.PNormNormalizationFactory, PolynomialTransform.PolyTransformFactory, ReliefF.ReliefFFactory, RemoveAttributeTransform.RemoveAttributeTransformFactory, SBS.SBSFactory, SFS.SFSFactory, UnitVarianceTransform.UnitVarianceTransformFactory, WhitenedPCA.WhitenedPCATransformFactory, WhitenedZCA.WhitenedZCATransformFactory, ZeroMeanTransform.ZeroMeanTransformFactory

    public interface DataTransformFactory
    It may be necessary to learn the same transform from several different versions of a data set, this interface facilitates that process.

        DataTransform getTransform(DataSet dataset)
        Creates a new transform that is inferred from the given data set
        Parameters:
        dataset - the data set to learn the transform from
        Returns:
        a new DataTransform that can be used
        Throws:
        FailedToFitException - if the transform could not be constructed or was inappropriate for the given data set.
